itunes:title: Called to Be Loved - Part 1
title: Called to Be Loved - Part 1
description: God not only knows where you are; he also knows who you are. He knows what you’re going through, why you’re going through it, and how you feel about it. He knows you better than you know yourself! Pastor Rick uses this message to help you understand just how much Jesus wants to affirm you and show you his love.
